text: Maximiliano Alejandro Velasco (born 19 June 1990) is an Argentine football player. He plays for César Vallejo in the Peruvian Primera División. ==Club career== He made his Argentine Primera División debut for Newell's Old Boys on 11 June 2011 in a game against Olimpo. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 births Category:People from Villa María Category:Sportspeople from Córdoba Province, Argentina Category:Living people Category:Argentine footballers Category:Argentine expatriate footballers Category:Newell's Old Boys footballers Category:Talleres de Córdoba footballers Category:Sportivo Belgrano footballers Category:San Martín de Tucumán footballers Category:Universidad San Martín footballers Category:Deportivo Municipal footballers Category:Sport Boys footballers Category:Valletta F.C. players Category:Guabirá players Category:Club Deportivo Universidad César Vallejo footballers Category:Bolivian Primera División players Category:Argentine Primera División players Category:Primera B Nacional players Category:Peruvian Primera División players Category:Maltese Premier League players Category:Argentine expatriate sportspeople in Peru Category:Argentine expatriate sportspeople in Malta Category:Argentine expatriate sportspeople in Bolivia Category:Expatriate footballers in Peru Category:Expatriate footballers in Malta Category:Expatriate footballers in Bolivia Category:Association football forwards
